@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>We at Battleship Game value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our game.</p>
    
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p> &emsp; <strong>1. </strong>Personal Information: We do not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or contact details.</p>
    <p> &emsp; <strong>2. </strong>Gameplay Data: We may collect data related to your gameplay such as moves, game progress, and scores to improve your gaming experience.</p>
    
    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p> &emsp; <strong>1. </strong>Gameplay Enhancement: The data collected is used to improve game functionality and provide a better user experience.</p>
    <p> &emsp; <strong>2. </strong>Technical Support: Information may be used to diagnose technical issues and provide support.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not share your personal data with third parties, except as required by law or to protect the rights and safety of our users.</p>
    
    <p>By using our game, you consent to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.</p>
</body>
</html>

